description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JUN-13-2014 FRI...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program




  The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      Rep. Louie Gohmert On The Absurdity Of GOP Leadership 6/13/14


Friday, June 13, 2014 


The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET
Facebook: Glenn Beck
Twitter: @glennbeck



Glenn asks if America is already in a civil war,

    encourages people to stand together with others who are good,
 
      and sheds light on the significant number of crises the nation 
 
       has experienced so far this year. 

Rep. Louie Gohmert joins the program to discuss border chaos
                                      and Republican leadership,

 and 17-year-old Abby Anderson joins Glenn to discuss her incredible song.



             That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
